{"id":3008,"date":"2021-07-28T20:00:39","date_gmt":"2021-07-28T13:00:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/?p=3008"},"modified":"2023-11-23T09:23:10","modified_gmt":"2023-11-23T02:23:10","slug":"di-dinh-cu-canada-duoc-mang-bao-nhieu-tien-neu-mang-qua-nhieu-thi-sao","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/di-dinh-cu-canada-duoc-mang-bao-nhieu-tien-neu-mang-qua-nhieu-thi-sao\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110i \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n? N\u1ebfu mang qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00ec sao?"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_63 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >N\u1ed9i dung b&agrave;i vi\u1ebft<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/di-dinh-cu-canada-duoc-mang-bao-nhieu-tien-neu-mang-qua-nhieu-thi-sao\/#1_Dinh_cu_Canada_duoc_mang_bao_nhieu_tien\" title=\"1. \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n?\">1. \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/di-dinh-cu-canada-duoc-mang-bao-nhieu-tien-neu-mang-qua-nhieu-thi-sao\/#2_Neu_can_mang_qua_Canada_nhieu_tien_thi_lam_the_nao\" title=\"2. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n mang qua Canada nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n th\u00ec l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?\">2. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n mang qua Canada nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n th\u00ec l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">\u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 xoay quanh, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i <b>\u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n?<\/b> l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft. C\u00f9ng ALLY t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada. \u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"h.6mehm8md7l42\" class=\"c7\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Dinh_cu_Canada_duoc_mang_bao_nhieu_tien\"><\/span><span class=\"c5\">1. \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh h\u00e0nh l\u00fd mang theo, ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu khi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang theo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n theo \u0111\u00fang quy \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh ph\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf l\u00e1 phong n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, khi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang theo t\u1ed1i \u0111a l\u00e0 10.000 CAD ~ 7.000 USD m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n khai b\u00e1o trong Declaration Card (t\u1edd khai nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh).<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c0\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/img_60fff0f9a105b.png\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Tuy v\u1eady, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang h\u01a1n 10.000 CAD khi qua Canada n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 khai b\u00e1o ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec1n h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p trong b\u1ea3n Declaration Card. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh mang qu\u00e1 10.000 CAD khi \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng khai b\u00e1o th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb 250CAD \u2013 5.000CAD v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ebd b\u1ecb l\u01b0u trong Passport r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng trung th\u1ef1c khi nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh Canada. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho b\u1ea1n xin gia h\u1ea1n visa ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m l\u1ea1i visa trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"h.vxkjsgvm9s5c\" class=\"c7\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Neu_can_mang_qua_Canada_nhieu_tien_thi_lam_the_nao\"><\/span><span class=\"c5\">2. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n mang qua Canada nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n th\u00ec l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n mang theo nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada th\u00ec sao? H\u00e3y n\u1ea1p s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y v\u00e0o th\u1ebb t\u00edn d\u1ee5ng ho\u1eb7c ATM qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. Sau khi qua t\u1edbi Canada, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ti\u1ec1n ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. C\u00e1ch n\u00e0y c\u0169ng tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1edbp khi mang qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t b\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n l\u1edbn \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m l\u00e0 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n Vi\u1ec7t sang ngo\u1ea1i t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 mang sang Canada. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam qua \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada, Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i ngo\u1ea1i t\u1ec7 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c0\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/img_60fff0fc1187f.png\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul class=\"c4 lst-kix_gkigu7shce5q-0 start\">\n<li class=\"c0 c2 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c1\">B\u1ea3n sao h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"c0 c2 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c1\">\u0110\u01a1n xin chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 mang ngo\u1ea1i t\u1ec7 sang Canada<\/span><\/li>\n<li class=\"c0 c2 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c1\">V\u0103n b\u1ea3n cho ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada (k\u00e8m b\u1ea3n d\u1ecbch x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 quan d\u1ecbch thu\u1eadt) t\u1eeb ph\u00eda c\u01a1 quan c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Canada. Ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea3n sao c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf Canada<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd n\u00eau tr\u00ean th\u00ec h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ph\u00eda ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn chi ti\u1ebft v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 mang ngo\u1ea1i t\u1ec7 sang Canada c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c1\">Nh\u00ecn chung, v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111i \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n? B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang theo s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t t\u1ed1i \u0111a l\u00e0 10.000 CAD, kho\u1ea3n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0o th\u1ebb ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed5i sang ngo\u1ea1i t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em qua Canada.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c0\"><span class=\"c9\">Hi<\/span><span class=\"c1\">\u00a0v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafc m\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi <a href=\"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/dinh-cu-canada-dien-tay-nghe\/\">\u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf Canada<\/a>. Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ph\u00e2n v\u00e2n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c xoay quanh vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00fa nh\u00e2n Canada th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. H\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi <span style=\"color: #173d6e;\"><strong>ALLY &#8211; \u0110\u01a1n V\u1ecb Chuy\u00ean T\u01b0 V\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ecbnh C\u01b0 v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea7u T\u01b0 Canada<\/strong><\/span>, v\u1edbi s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh gi\u00fap <span style=\"color: #173d6e;\"><strong>HI\u1ec6N TH\u1ef0C H\u00d3A GI\u1ea4C M\u01a0 \u0110\u1ecaNH C\u01af CANADA C\u1ee6A B\u1ea0N<\/strong><\/span> \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. T\u1ea1i ALLY, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1eadn t\u00e2m v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ef1c, l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 an to\u00e0n, \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif; font-size: 15.04px; background-color: #fdfdf9;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #173d6e;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">TH\u00d4NG TIN LI\u00caN H\u1ec6<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif; font-size: 15.04px; background-color: #fdfdf9;\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\ud83c\udfe2 HCM Office: <\/span><span style=\"text-transform: uppercase; color: #333333; font-family: Arial, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif; font-size: 14.4px; background-color: #ffffff;\">V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng 03, T\u1ea7ng 22, To\u00e0 nh\u00e0 Opal, s\u1ed1 92 Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu C\u1ea3nh, ph\u01b0\u1eddng 22, qu\u1eadn B\u00ecnh Th\u1ea1nh, TP. HCM<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif; font-size: 15.04px; background-color: #fdfdf9;\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\ud83d\udce7 \u00a0Email: info@aiic.vn<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif; font-size: 15.04px; background-color: #fdfdf9;\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\ud83c\udf10 \u00a0Website: https:\/\/aiic.vn<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"c1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.3em; margin-top: 0px; color: #777777; font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif; font-size: 15.04px; background-color: #fdfdf9;\"><span class=\"c0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\u260e Hotline: 028 9998 9988 \/ 0909 34 8899<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada hi\u1ec7n nay l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 xoay quanh, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c \u0111i \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 Canada \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mang bao nhi\u00eau ti\u1ec1n? l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft. C\u00f9ng<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":3009,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[80],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3008"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/6"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3008"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3008\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9100,"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3008\/revisions\/9100"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3009"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3008"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3008"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aiic.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3008"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}